s (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SBUX\" title=\"Starbucks Corporation\">SBUX</a></span>) as I believe the recent spike in coffee bean prices will further pressure Starbucks margin in the next</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743016-starbucks-gamble-low-hedge-ratio-amid-surging-green-coffee-prices-strong-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:16:51"}, {"id": "4742932", "title": "Main Street Vs. Fidus Investment: Both Are Top Class, One Is At Better Price", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A couple under a red umbrella. Health and life insurance concept.\" data-id=\"1956825007\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1027px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw -