ps://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital Brain With Connections\" data-id=\"2107031844\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>While ClearPoint's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CLPT\" title=\"ClearPoint Neuro, Inc.\">CLPT</a></span>) share price has stagnated in recent months, even as the broader market has surged higher, there have been a number of positive developments. In particular, ClearPoint's laser therapy and drug delivery businesses appear set to continue driving strong</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743007-clearpoint-fundamentals-continue-to-improve", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:50:34"}, {"id": "4743020", "title": "VersaBank 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by VersaBank in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106079\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743020-versabank-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:36:14"}, {"id": "4742943", "title": "Retail Sector Earnings Roundup: Analyzing The Holiday Season Winners And Losers", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Shop owner handing bag to smiling client after shopping in clothing boutique\" data-id=\"1217476252\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The holiday shopping season is in full swing, and a broad range of retailers have reported results, with many surpassing sales and earnings expectations. The macroeconomic environment continues to favor retailers with a strong value-driven product mix, benefiting giants like Walmart (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742943-retail-sector-earnings-roundup-analyzing-the-holiday-season-winners-and-losers", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:30:00"}, {"id": "4742835", "title": "1 REIT To Sell And 1 Strong Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sold sign in front yard of house\" data-id=\"109350551\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109350551/image_109350551.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://st